Feeling very grateful to have attended the DKMS Gala last night with @covergirl @sally_hansen and founding sponsor, @cotyinc, alongside @verawang @priyankachopra @cocorocha @marcjacobs! There were many heartfelt moments that reminded me why their mission to #deletebloodcancer is so important.  Did you know that every 3 minutes, someone is diagnosed with #bloodcancer in the US? That’s why DKMS has made it their mission to spread hope and save lives. They are an international non-profit organization dedicated to the fight against blood cancers and disorders by creating awareness, recruiting bone marrow donors to provide a second chance at life, raising funds, and supporting the improvement of blood cancer therapies.  Here’s how you can support @dkms_us:

1. Register as a potential donor: It’s free and easy, you can simply swab your cheeks at home.  Just register at DKMS—the link is in my bio. 

2. Share this post and spread the word!

3. Make a donation to help DKMS continue their lifesaving work

Each one of us has the power to make a difference! #DKMS

Thank you @covergirl & @sally_hansen for partnering with me—it was an honor!
